{"tid":2347979,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★\"農夫山泉\" 鍾睒睒登上中國首富第1位\" 拼多多\"黃崢 第2位 力壓去年的 馬雲及馬化騰","createTime":"2020-12-31T11:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T12:24:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"52801d6ff219e625d8e6cca3568e7c69bd420c50","tid":2347979,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"中國首富排名2020年大執位，總結全年，農夫山泉(09633)創辦人鍾睒睒登上中國首富之位，超越印度首富安巴尼(Mukesh Ambani)成為亞洲首富，全球首富榜則排名第8位；而在美國上市的 ，其創辦人黃崢排名中國首富榜第2位，與首席的鍾睒睒，力壓去年的冠、亞軍馬雲及馬化騰。<br />\n<br />\n據《福布斯》中國富豪榜單資料顯示，現年66歲的鍾睒睒財富飆升786億美元(約6,130億港元)。農夫山泉是內地包裝飲用水及飲料龍頭企業，今年9月在香港上市，招股價21.5元，首日掛牌收市報33.1元，升53.95%；股價隨後節節上升，周三(12月30日)股價高見56.5元再創新高，周四(12月31日)收市報54.9元，升0.09%。上市以來，農夫山泉股價累計已升1.55倍，市值已突破2,700億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/fov/bkn-20201231163347753-1231_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Fcontent%2Ffov%2Fbkn-20201231163347753-1231_00842_001.html&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmySthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=d63beaee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/fov/bkn-20201231163347753-1231_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e0ff9da7154fafd0ef4172c282cc2d398c565755","tid":2347979,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nreturn blood"},{"pid":"40761d5ca3b548d618e00b1fe656152f600a1bb5","tid":2347979,"uid":321002,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"等割韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji